org.magnos.stat
Class StatPoint

All Implemented Interfaces:
org.magnos.data.Data
public class StatPoint
extends org.magnos.data.DataSet

A single statistical point in an archive. A point can hold several statistics by keeping a running summary of the statistics added to the point:

  1. Total statistics added to the point
  2. The sum of the statistics
  3. The average of the statistics (sum / total)
  4. The smallest statistic added
  5. The largest statistic added

Author:
Philip Diffenderfer
